high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the fridge, turn right, go forward to the counter with the toaster.
Take the bowl from the cabinet below the counter with the toaster.
Turn around, go forward, turn right to the fridge.
Chill the bowl to the left of the apple in the fridge. Take the bowl from the fridge.
Take a step back from the fridge, look up above the fridge.
Put the bowl in the cabinet above the right side of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in a cabinet above a fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the refrigerator, turn right for two steps and stop.
Open the bottom right cabinet door, directly under the knife; pull out the silver bowl and shut the cabinet door.
Turn right for one step then turn right again for three steps, turn right to face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator and put the bowl on the top shelf to the left of the orange and then shut the door for a few seconds, open the door, take the bowl out and shut the door.
Turn around and take one step, turn back around  to face the fridge and then hold the bowl close to the top of the fridge.
Open the cabinet above the right side of the fridge and put the bowl in the bottom left part of the cabinet and then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled silver bowl in the cabinet above the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge, then turn right and walk to the toaster.
Take the bowl out of he bottom right cabinet below the counter with the toaster on it.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the bowl in the fridge to the left of the apple. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the bowl in the cabinet on top and to the right of the fridge, on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled bowl in a cabinet.
